Not all DDR ram is the same.  I would go with Crucial 2100 DDR ram.  Going cheap now.  WWW.Crucial.com<br>
<br>
You might want to think about upgradeing your system.  Maybe a celeron.  Update your bios first and see what level of celeron it supports.  Then just get a converter card and you are set.<br>
